---
interface Props {
  id?: string;
}

const { id = "testimonial-section" } = Astro.props;
---

<section id={id} class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-16 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-8">
      Stop Guessing And Start Learning
    </h2>
    
    <div class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-12 space-y-6">
      <p>
        We understand what it feels like trying to learn PDR. Standing on the outside looking in. Never sure if you're doing it right. There is a better way to learn Paintless Dent Repair. Real World PDR Ultimate was created to be your man on the inside. Helping you learn the skills and techniques needed to stand out in the industry. We've trained hundreds of PDR technicians to be successful and we can train you too.
      </p>
      <p>
        Get on the road to your new career today. Click "GET INSTANT ACCESS" and start learning right away!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8 mb-12">
      <blockquote class="text-lg md:text-xl italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
        "Jim is as masterful with his words as he is with his repairs. Being a seasoned tech I only wish I would have had someone to train me from the beginning that would have cut through all the nonsense and actually broke it down to the real usable knowledge. His videos are honest and packed with priceless repeatable knowledge, not only beginners but for any open minded tech that is willing to grow. His ability to verbally break down the process made me have a new view on large collision."
      </blockquote>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6">
        <img 
          src="/api/files/sites/proj_dkm43vn7/1776723863099/assets/mo7rijiyemw9t8.jpg" 
          alt="Tom Poland testimonial"
          class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="font-semibold text-xl">Tom Poland</div>
          <div class="text-gray-400">Midwest Auto Dent Repair</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a 
        href="https://realworldpdr.thinkific.com/cart/add_product/446304?price_id=467664"
        class="inline-block bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg text-lg transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        SUBSCRIBE TO PDR ULTIMATE
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
